 break-word !important;">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">术后病人</span></strong><br data-filtered="filtered" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　促进伤口愈合、恢复病人体质、清热解毒、消炎杀菌。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">三高人群</strong></span></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　高血脂：提高细胞修复能力，帮助血液快速清毒，促进肝脏排毒，使肝细胞加速修复，辅助降低血脂、血压胆固醇。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　高血压：抑制血管紧张素转化酶（ACE）的活性从而使血压降低。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　高血糖：激活胰岛分泌、调节血糖。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">心脑血管疾病</strong></span></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-heig