; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">胃溃疡人群</strong></span></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　胃溃疡其实是胃粘膜受损后引起的胃表皮组织损伤，肽系列可以促进胃表皮伤口生长愈合，达到修复的作用。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">皮肤问题人群</strong></span></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　有效祛除自由基，抗氧化，抗辐射，抗湿疹，淡化色斑，提亮皮肤。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">肾功能减退人群</strong></span></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　肾炎、痛风、尿毒症人群一般不能吃豆制品，但又非常需要蛋白质的摄入，肽系列已祛除了嘌呤等有害物质，小分子肽可以直接为人体吸收而不加重肾脏的负荷，直接修复受损细胞和脏器。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">　　<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">肝功能不全者</span></strong></p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">　　提高肝细胞修复能力，帮助血液快速清毒，促进肝脏排毒，调节肝脏病人血液中的氨基酸，改善肝功能。</p><p hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" line-height:="" background-color:="" box-sizing:="" border-box="" word-wrap:="" break-word="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br style="margin: 